              <h2>Advertise with SyncIT.com</h2>
              <h3>Why should I advertise on SyncIT? </h3>
              <p>SyncIT users are technologically advanced, quick to adopt, and 
                primarily web developers or internet veterans who average more 
                than 500 bookmarks per person. Furthermore, SyncIT can target 
                your advertising towards users with specific interests, guaranteeing 
                a higher response than from advertising to the general public. 
              </p>
              <h3>How do I advertise on SyncIT? </h3>
              <h4>Free Campaigns </h4>
              <ol>
                <li> One-to-one banner exchange: For every banner of yours that 
                  we display, you display one of our banners. <br>
                  <br>
                </li>
                
              <li> Mutual Traffic Partnerships: See <b><a href="partner.asp">Partner 
                with SyncIT </a></b>page for details. </li>
              </ol>
              <h4>Paid Campaigns </h4>
              <ol>
                <li> Affiliate advertising: If you have an affiliate program that 
                  rewards referrals or e-commerce, we will rotate your banner 
                  at your affiliate rates. Your advantage is that your banner/logo 
                  will be visible on multiple pages through our website. <br>
                  <br>
                </li>
                <li> Interactive Mini-banner: Advertise on our mini-banner at 
                  a competitive CPM rate. <br>
                  <br>
                  The SyncIT mini-banner is a new and innovative way to display 
                  your brand to internet users. Unlike traditional banners which 
                  are easily ignored, the mini-banner is an interactive tool which 
                  does not limit your advertising to one dimension. A recent Forrester 
                  report, "Branding Divorces Advertising," finds that the effectiveness 
                  of banner ads have declined and attributes this to: "The model 
                  of delivering a single brand message to a mass audience...crumbling 
                  under the pressures of results-focused advertisers and declining 
                  media audiences." <br>
                  <br>
                  The SyncIT mini-banner is the new solution. The mini-banner 
                  format allows direct links to content on your website. You can 
                  link to your latest product, play up features or services that 
                  are not well-known, and provide users direct access to your 
                  registration page. The success of the mini-banner is proven 
                  by data that shows the amount of interactivity with the mini-banner 
                  is nine times the number of page view hits. Best of all, the 
                  mini-banner is available on the desktop, not the web page, and 
                  does not require a user to be online to receive the message. 
                </li>
              </ol>
